::Hot Rod::

He saw Windlord land. He quickly ran infront of him, putting his body
between Windlord and the incoming Alliance troops. He fired in their
general direction, even though most wern't there yet.

::Dollen::

He gets in StarScream.
"I dont think those guys will fit, but they can hold on to you."
He looks at Killfests group.
"Grab on! We're getting out of here!"
